              ></path>
            </svg>
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="swap-off h-5 w-5 fill-current"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                d="M21.64,13a1,1,0,0,0-1.05-.14,8.05,8.05,0,0,1-3.37.73A8.15,8.15,0,0,1,9.08,5.49a8.59,8.59,0,0,1,.25-2A1,1,0,0,0,8,2.36,10.14,10.14,0,1,0,22,14.05,1,1,0,0,0,21.64,13Zm-9.5,6.69A8.14,8.14,0,0,1,7.08,5.22v.27A10.15,10.15,0,0,0,17.22,15.63a9.79,9.79,0,0,0,2.1-.22A8.11,8.11,0,0,1,12.14,19.73Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </label>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/BitB0y/bgp.mom"
            class="btn btn-ghost"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- After the navbar -->
    <div class="alert alert-error alert-soft">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex items-start gap-2">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <p class="text-sm">
          List of recommended providers for newbies/hobbyists. Want to be added?
          <a href="https://github.com/Bitti09/bgp.mom/issues" class="underline"
            >Open issue on GitHub</a
          >.
          <span class="block font-bold mt-1">
            Please note: This project does not initiate communication via
            support tickets or live chat. Any individual claiming to be an
            'auditor' for us is fraudulent.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <main class="w-full py-8 flex-1">
      <slot />
    </main>

    <footer class="footer footer-center p-4 bg-base-200 text-base-content mt-8">
      <div>
        <p>Made with â™¥ by the BGP Community</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  @import "flag-icons/css/flag-icons.min.css";

  :root {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  }

  /* Ensure footer stays at bottom */
  html,
  body {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  main {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .menu .disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .menu .disabled:hover {
    background: none;
  }
</style>
